item.title: Compling error :S help
item.dc:creator: @1337_king 1337 king
item.description:
@1337_king wrote:

Do you have the latest java development kit installed?
If not, then go to http://www.sun.com/ and download the latest JDK

If you have, then go to its folder, C:/Programfiles/Java/JDK…/Bin/
COPY all your .java files there, and the compiler.bat
run the compiler there, and it should work.

After its done, and no errors, you have to copy back in your server folder the made .class files.

Simple;)
